Package: tdna
Type: Package
Title: Query and Plot Arabidopsis T-DNA Insertions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Grey", family = "Monroe", role = c("aut", "cre"),
               email = "yourself@somewhere.net"))
Description: Provides helper functions to look up and visualise confirmed
    homozygous T-DNA insertion lines within Arabidopsis genes. The package
    ships with annotation tables from public resources and allows users to
    query and plot insertions for a given gene.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: data.table, ggplot2, ggrepel
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
